wikipedia_page.main: Charles Fane de Salis  (1860–1942) was Bishop of Taunton from 1911 to 1930.

response: *19311942 (d.): Charles de Salis, Archdeacon of Taunton until 1938, and former Bishop of Taunton
*1911–1938 (ret.): Charles de Salis, Bishop suffragan of Taunton (until 1930) then assistant bishop
